Job Summary:
To support operational and closing activities for Singapore HQ, Sub-Business Unit.
The individual will ensure accurate &amp; timely preparation of all finance information, especially month end management accounts and input towards budget/forecast submissions in conjunction with the Finance &amp; Admin Team Lead.

Responsibilities:

  Assist in the monthly closing of Singapore entity and consolidation of group accounts.
  Maintaining full set of accounts for sub-business unit with supporting schedules.
  Preparation of Inter-company Reconciliations and other Balance sheet schedules.
  Assist in preparation of annual budget/forecast exercises.
  Preparation of GST returns, &amp; other Government returns as required.
  Assisting in annual external audits
  Any Ad hoc task assigned by supervisor
